        "subtext": "A clean, scalable Model-View-Controller (MVC) approach.",
        "body": "The application is driven by a central state machine in main.js (Controller). Project and content data is decoupled into JSON files (Model), allowing for easy updates without touching the logic. Visual components are encapsulated into classes like GalaxyView and SolarSystemView (View), ensuring a clean separation of concerns."
